            <title>Apple 首次卖 USB-A 至 USB-C 线，每条盛惠 $148 元</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/07/apple-50/mobile-phone/phone-parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-50</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/07/apple-50/mobile-phone/phone-parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[毛]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 06:29:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手机配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 充电线]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone15]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1197479</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 早前推出的 iPhone 15 系列为 Apple 第一款使用 USB-C 充电的电话，在 iPhone 15 发布后 Apple 终于在官网售卖 USB-A 至 USB-C 线，售价为每条 $148 元。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-07-下午 2.28.25.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197936" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-07-下午 2.28.25-694x451.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="451" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-07-下午 2.28.25-694x451.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-07-下午 2.28.25-1280x831.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-07-下午 2.28.25-768x499.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-07-下午 2.28.25-1536x998.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-07-下午 2.28.25.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>本周， Apple 在官网中新增了 BOOST↑Charge Pro Flex USB-A 至 USB-C 连接线 (1 米)。Apple 称 Boost Charge Pro Flex 的耐用度比普通连接线高达 30 倍，不易磨损和缠绕，兼容支援 USB-C 的 Mac、iPad 或 iPhone；连接线亦随附一个磁力连接线整理器，使用更方便快捷。</p><p>Boost Charge Pro Flex 连接线现已可于 Apple 线上商店购买，订购最快下周三（11 日）送达，而现时仅提供 1 米长度、白色的款式。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1197488" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.02.08-PM-694x365.png" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.02.08-PM-694x365.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.02.08-PM-1280x673.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.02.08-PM-768x404.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.02.08-PM-1536x807.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-05-at-4.02.08-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>然而，在 Belkin 的官方网站亦能搜寻到这款同名连接线，同时更设有 4 款的颜色及提供 1 米、2 米，和 3 米三款长度供用户选择。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk-zh/shop/product/HQZQ2ZM/A/boost↑charge-pro-flex-usb-a-至-usb-c-连接线-1-米">Apple</a>、<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2023/10/04/iphone-15-usb-a-to-usb-c-cable/?fbclid=IwAR1C5CaTquKR6lrhuOSYtRFHNKtmwEXyiefgHd0kEOjiOEdZCiJ4I8qmoxA">9To5Mac</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
